<th><a href="Fricative_consonant" title="Fricative consonant">Fricative</a></th>
<td></td>
<td></td>
<td style="text-align:center;"><b><span title="Representation in the International Phonetic Alphabet (IPA)" class="IPA">f</span></b></td>
<td><i><span title="Representation in the International Phonetic Alphabet (IPA)" class="IPA">v</span></i></td>
<td style="text-align:center;">((<span title="Representation in the International Phonetic Alphabet (IPA)" class="IPA">θ</span>))</td>
<td></td>
